sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Next.js Sender 
    participant API as NestJS Chat API / Socket
    participant Queue as BullMQ 
    participant Worker as Persistence Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    actor Others as Room Members

    Note over User, Others: All Connected (connect)

    Note right of User: Writes message
    Note left of User: Optimistically update UI
    
    User->>API: HTTP POST /messages

    activate API

    Note over API, Queue: Async Persistence Job
    API-->>Queue: Add persistence job
    API-->>User: 202 Accepted

    deactivate API

    activate Worker

    Note over Queue, DB: Background Processing
    Worker->>Queue: Process job
    Worker->>DB: Save message
    DB-->>Worker: Success
    
    Note over Worker, User: Broadcast via WebSocket
    Worker->>API: Job complete
    
    deactivate Worker
    
    API->>User: emit "msg:received" (confirm)
    API->>Others: emit "msg:received" (new message to connected sockets)
    
    Note left of User: Mark as Persisted
    Note right of Others: Display new message